    About the Business

    Business owner information

    Emma H.

    Business Owner

    We make simply the best, most wholesome baked goods in South City. Specializing in both sweet and savory breakfast items, tea cookies, oatmeal cream pies, cupcakes, custom cakes and more. Top it all off with Kaldi's coffee & our housemade syrups and there isn't much more you could ask for!…

    • Q:

      Why is this bakery in Yelp's top ten sugar-free bakeries for 2022? Do they actually have any sugar-free pastries available?

      A:

      We are wondering why as well! I’m not sure any of those bakeries are sugar free. We are NOT. FYI we had no part in this list and are not sure how it was created.

      Emma H., Business Owner
